title: Earl Thomas holding out, Chiefs/Jags outlooks, Top 100 players (Football 06/12)
description:
Pete Prisco is joined by former NFL cornerback Bryant McFadden to discuss Earl Thomas holding out of the Seahawks' mandatory minicamp and if there should be concern in Seattle. The guys also breakdown the importance of minicamps, where the Chiefs rank in the AFC West and the make-or-break nature of the Jaguars upcoming 2018 season. Pete and Bryant finish by reacting to Pete's list of the Top 100 players in the NFL, focusing on the Top 10.
